Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:34.32,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon pages and pages of entries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:38.46,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've put down all our emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:41.75,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I've hit a writer's block
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:45.72,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to finish this page anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.91,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting a bookmark in my diary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:53.95,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I go out to ride the bike we found in the dumpster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:57.11,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to our secret place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:01.45,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we piled up our bricks of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:06.71,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Run up the hill, where we can see the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:11.25,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we can see the sky so fearfully blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:14.47,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,With cider in my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.98,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,My other hand helps me search for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:23.10,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to come find me way back when
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.79,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to demand me of so much more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:33.57,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both still standing right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:41.35,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet why do I pray to see you both again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:49.46,Opening 2,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something off with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.58,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}deai wa futtoshita shunkan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:54.21,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kaerimichi no kousaten de koe wo kaketekureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"issho ni kaerou"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:05.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ureshikute tanoshikute bouken mo iro iro shita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:12.13,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}futari no himitsu no kichi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:19.64,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kimi to natsu no owari shourai no yume ookina kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:26.74,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}jyuunen no ato hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:33.95,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kimi ga saigo made kokoro kara "arigatou" sakendeita koto shitetayo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:36.77,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}namida wo koraete egao
