Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:48.24,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.58,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We met in an unexpected moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:54.21,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,when you called out to me at the crosswalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's walk home together."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:05.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We shared so many happy times and thrilling adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:12.13,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,together in our secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:19.64,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams we shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:26.74,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we will meet again in another August, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:33.95,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:36.77,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know it must've been painful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:41.03,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:48.24,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But those are my best memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.21,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.26,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:34.47,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:35.77,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:38.21,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.90,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he nagging me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.82,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I prefer it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.23,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,No, it would be better if he did nag me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:57.16,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:58.83,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay Anaru back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:03.20,Alt,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:08.88,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.39,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So you were listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:18.53,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I helped you collect all the Nokemon, so you can't break your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:20.31,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:26.53,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That might be my wish - having you go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:31.51,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what this is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.99,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.58,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Get out. I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.96,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly appeared in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.80,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She pushed some senseless request onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.13,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She's the beast of summer. My hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.26,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:03.68,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to have my wish granted. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:09.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually early fall going by the calendar, \Nbut the beast of summer has stayed in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.08,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being driven out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.55,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.65,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,No choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.57,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...but to go to school.
