Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.05,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.08,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I should just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.23,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You came to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.40,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.23,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.86,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it's not because you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.37,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.37,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, is that really Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.22,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you really came to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.34,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Aki, Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.75,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin' Naruko, Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:20.39,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright! Nobody cares that you skipped a semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.72,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, nobody cared about you in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.97,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Ice burn, Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.53,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's enough{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:32.06,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,The power of love is really something. \NThis is all because you went to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.48,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,That's so hot. Their love is ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:37.49,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Who'd want a guy like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.48,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.90,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.85,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for the heat getting to my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:52.49,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have bothered coming to this idiot zoo they call a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.44,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Jin{\fscx250}-{\r} Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.44,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,He's going home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:06:00.69,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, was that supposed to be an insult? {lit. insult upon leaving/last remark}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.76,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.01,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Being home alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.18,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,...is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.44,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.26,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Time to explore Jintan's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:25.13,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, how about this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.76,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.03,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:35.41,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan's mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.75,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,She was way prettier in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:45.28,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like the picture my family has of me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:49.37,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But I always made the 'peace' sign when I got my photo taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:52.97,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,so there probably weren't any normal photos of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:02.45,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead too, but right now I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.11,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.25,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm crying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.99,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan will get angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.54,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,This is pathetic. 	{they're pathetic?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.30,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with my promise to Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.22,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, my hallucination, is telling me to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.93,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That means somewhere inside of me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.18,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.77,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.70,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,{Poppo is chanting in germannordicmagicspeak, not japanese}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.95,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.17,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.72,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.10,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I saw too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.13,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.97,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:19.43,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting pretty awesome myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.43,Alt,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my hallucination...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.95,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It was a miracle of timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.73,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I made a miraculous curved shape with my piss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.59,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,And then it was like... woah, a triangle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.38,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Something appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.99,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you didn't mistake something else for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.05,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I've got the eyesight of an Ottoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:42.01,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's become a grown woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.82,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She's grown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:46.21,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's a fine woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.74,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What was she wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.43,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,That white one-piece dress that she often wore during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:58.13,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma came back to have her wish granted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:01.39,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get serious and put all my effort into figuring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.32,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.55,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner? It's still noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.18,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be? Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.40,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Curry steamed for eight hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.51,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I want some too! Hey Jintan, let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:19.33,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.93,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,The grown-up Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.14,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.46,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.62,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch that. You're actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.77,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're really early, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:51.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,All we had today was the opening \Nceremony, so school was out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.11,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.61,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.48,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I applied my home ec knowledge! {home economics; I tried doing chores}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.49,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the mess you've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.15,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that..?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.38,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.21,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.61,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me, Poppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.38,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, are there any ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta. You came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.03,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.52,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.70,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to eat your muffins. {lit. steamed bread, but come on, they're muffins}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.20,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta. Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.66,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.41,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.56,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.43,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:07.77,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.85,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:21.49,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,The ones your mom made were tastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.71,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I didn't have any raisins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.88,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll practice more and more, and I'll make them even tastier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:32.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,More? Do you plan on staying here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.55,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.82,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.84,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you go over to Poppo's place too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I've been at home this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.28,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.74,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that was my ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.71,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So what does that make you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.52,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Meiko Honma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.89,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,This is so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:03.36,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter whether you're a ghost or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.38,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,There's egg shell in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.32,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm... that's for the calcium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:27.29,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't decide? I have things to do too you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,My bad. Wait just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:35.56,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.77,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hisakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.94,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hisakawa... you mean Poppo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.15,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,So you still keep in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.29,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,He found Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.53,Default,Sale,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.25,Default,Sale,0000,0000,0000,,You must be his girlfriend. I'm so envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:57.23,Default,Sale,0000,0000,0000,,We have a wide selection, so please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.71,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're always taking me places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.14,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Who's it for? {lit. who are you supporting; think it refers to his menma fetish}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.84,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.40,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Alright already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.22,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a subscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.74,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:29.03,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's Search Party to commemorate the end of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.81,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, a cool evening and a barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.88,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the point of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.85,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah yeah yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.47,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you have to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.26,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I have to? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.55,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.40,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.68,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I want to search for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.31,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.79,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Then say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:55.62,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:59.83,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the wish I wanted to be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:03.52,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I might have wanted to see my own ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:08.11,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at making wishes that fit the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.60,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Naruko. Let's go to karaoke on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.71,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll pass tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:45.57,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure mini-sausages are enough for a barbecue? {lit. Bavarian sausages}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:49.07,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I had in the fridge that I could bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.53,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Someone'll probably bring something anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.74,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,We also have my muffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.86,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.96,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:08.24,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Look Jintan, it's Anaru! Let's go together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:13.83,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jintan! Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:17.06,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.27,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.50,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.54,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.60,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.77,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,For the past while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:40.91,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.28,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.18,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Jintan! You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.76,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get along and go as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.13,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,He made such a scene falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.30,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the same place anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.43,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.45,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.83,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so cute with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.35,Alt,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo, you called Tsuruk... Tsurumi too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.59,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you read the ad I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.49,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,When I wrote everyone, I meant everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.50,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.53,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Masala tea. {Indian}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:11.47,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You might mean everyone, but Yukiatsu probably won't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.48,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem like he believes in stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.32,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.43,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Raise that a bit higher, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.17,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.38,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.94,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this grill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.28,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed it from the old man at my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.83,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to grill? I just brought some sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.78,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I brought candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.44,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to summon Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.03,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd need some props appropriate for a ghost story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:42.86,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.77,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:47.21,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,So what about food for the barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:51.33,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't eat much at night, so don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:55.51,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. All Tsuruko thinks of is herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.98,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Selfish women turn me on, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:16:59.85,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.12,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.33,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everyone else would bring food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.64,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to bring the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.63,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.49,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,We're not children anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.26,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,And I have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.13,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.77,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It's called keel. {not sure what the english name for it is}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:23.72,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I ate it when I went to India. It's sweetened rice cooked in milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.40,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's like puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:30.09,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,So this isn't for a barbecue either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try frying it like okonomiyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.82,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stick to the sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,There, it finally caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.58,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It just didn't feel right without a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:48.30,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite the party we got here. It's been so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.60,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How do you make crabs again? {Anal crabs}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:55.06,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs? Can you make crabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.06,Alt,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,We're just like this charcoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.47,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.16,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally made by burning wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.03,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't light up right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.96,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,once it remembers it's past it roars ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.21,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's a terrible analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.89,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:17.22,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-should I help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:17.90,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.05,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:23.09,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But all we have are sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:25.07,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I already made cuts in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.79,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.73,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,A white one-piece dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Menma used to wear one often.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:40.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you said. I'm easily influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.77,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I always was, and I still am. I haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:49.61,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,And even though it's like Menma, she \Nwouldn't wear one with such a high cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:54.95,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,My friends from school wear ones like this, \Nbut they probably wouldn't pick a white one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:59.42,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I actually do put some thought into what I wear you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:02.09,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I end up going with the flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:05.08,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But for me... And in general, I do think a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.12,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you hope to gain by telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:15.05,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to say, "Is that so. How admirable."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.08,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.93,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.73,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted someone get on my case
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.47,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,for always going along with what's happening around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.06,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that Jintan! It's a crab, a crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.96,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,And there's an octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.05,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.52,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,This is authentic German sausage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.99,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.20,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You can tell too, Tsuruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.86,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it'd be so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.49,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:47.70,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan! Jintan! The crab will burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.70,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.84,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,So about Menma's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.34,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'll help us out too won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.03,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.26,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,The crab...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:09.22,Alt,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's OK to believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.91,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then I will as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:17.86,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll do it? Alright, Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.39,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jintan, the Super Peace Busters...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:22.65,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,The Super Peace Busters are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.72,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Super Peace? It's been a while since I've heard that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.07,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,It's super nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.75,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? We're all still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:35.46,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, I guess we never did retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.69,Alt,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:36.46,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.42,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:44.43,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,With things the way they are, do you think maybe Menma will get nostalgic too and suddenly come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.77,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What. This is quite a welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.48,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.43,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.68,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.13,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're Anjou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.13,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.74,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I brought vegetables and ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.28,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,And some herbal salt and olive oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.91,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.58,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,So you came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.98,Alt,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,You're so unlike a certain useless woman here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:09.70,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:14.84,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,But you really scared me there. I thought it was Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.19,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Menma a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.52,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.63,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:21.82,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Where was she? Where's Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.29,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Over there by the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.45,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Let's go, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.25,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.01,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.35,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it wasn't just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.19,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.42,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to see Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:54.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone is around... it's fun.
